2072215990178131927.Text: Right. That's Velfred's ship. It never comes into Hla Oad, but sometimes docks near here. Follow the coast southwest to get to Hla Oad's less public docks.

17009242251054913270.Text: Velfred never docks in Hla Oad, but he sells goods here from time to time. He must have another dock near here.
